underlying_goal: Commit and push updates to a research paper, including fixing aggregation methods and verifying experimental numbers.
primary_success: Claude accurately analyzed a large set of unstaged changes (27 files), correctly summarizing them into logical groups (plan updates, figure regenerations, paper corrections) before creating a concise and descriptive commit.
brief_summary: The user requested to commit changes related to a research paper. Claude analyzed the 27 modified/created files, identifying the key changes as fixes to the aggregation method (mean to median), verification of experimental numbers, and figure updates. Claude then successfully created a commit with a descriptive message.
